TSIU02
Computer Hardware and Architecture
Link√∂pings universitet
2021

Course content:

- Binary arithmetic: Number representations. Arithmetic-logical functions, addition, subtraction, multiplication, shifts.
- Computer architecture: Internal dataflow in a simple computer model. Instructions, instruction formats, addressing modes, input and output, exceptions.
- Input- and output peripherals. Ports, A/D-conversions.
- Mikrocontroller: Purpose and features. Built-in peripherals, timers, clocking alternatives, blackout och brownout.
